---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getDocBySlug } from '../../../data/navigation';

const doc = getDocBySlug('llm-gateway');

if (!doc) {
	throw new Error('LLM gateway doc metadata is missing');
}
---

<Layout title={`${doc.title} | 通俗版 Claude Code 文档`} description={doc.summary} pathname={doc.path}>
	<article class="space-y-8">
		<header class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em]" style="color: var(--muted);">Deployment</p>
			<h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-semibold">LLM gateway LLM 网关配置</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8">{doc.summary}</p>
			<p class="mt-4 max-w-4xl leading-8" style="color: var(--muted);">
				原页来源：
				<a href="https://code.claude.com/docs/en/llm-gateway" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="underline decoration-dotted underline-offset-4">官方 LLM gateway</a>
			</p>
		</header>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">一句人话</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>LLM 网关就是在你和 Claude 之间加个"中间人"，帮你管认证、限流、计费、审计。</p>
				<p>适合多团队共用、需要统一管控、集中看账单的场景。</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">啥时候用 LLM 网关</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p><strong>1. 多团队共用</strong> — 一个网关管所有团队的请求，统一认证。</p>
				<p><strong>2. 集中计费</strong> — 所有请求走一个账号，账单好看。</p>
				<p><strong>3. 限流配额</strong> — 给每个团队设配额，防止某个团队把额度用光。</p>
				<p><strong>4. 审计合规</strong> — 所有请求都经过网关，方便审计。</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">怎么配置</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>设置环境变量指向你的网关：</p>
				<div class="mt-4 rounded-[24px] border p-6 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
<pre># 指向自定义 LLM 网关
export ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://your-gateway.example.com/v1

# 如果用 Bedrock 网关
export ANTHROPIC_BEDROCK_BASE_URL=https://your-bedrock-gateway.example.com

# 如果用 Vertex AI 网关
export ANTHROPIC_VERTEX_BASE_URL=https://your-vertex-gateway.example.com</pre>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">常见网关方案</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8" style="color: var(--muted);">
				<p><strong>自研网关</strong> — 自己写个反向代理，加认证、限流逻辑。</p>
				<p><strong>开源方案</strong> — 用 LiteLLM、vLLM 等开源项目。</p>
				<p><strong>云服务</strong> — 用云厂商的 API 网关服务。</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">最后一句土话</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>LLM 网关就是个"二房东"，帮你管租户、收租金、记账本。小团队用不上，大团队才需要。</p>
				<p style="color: var(--muted);">别为了炫技上网关，直接用更简单便宜。</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</article>
</Layout>
